<html lang='en'>

  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        color: #495057; /* Slightly softer text color */
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 620px; /* Slightly wider for a more open feel */
        margin: 40px auto; /* More top/bottom margin */
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); /* Softer shadow */
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .header img {
        max-width: 160px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        font-size: 28px; /* Slightly larger for emphasis */
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-weight: 500; /* Slightly lighter font weight */
      }

      .content {
        padding: 25px 0;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 17px; /* Slightly larger for a warmer feel */
        color: #555555;
      }

      .content p {
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 35px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 35px; /* Slightly more padding */
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #ffffff;
        background-color: #28a745; /* A hopeful green color */
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #1e7e34; /* Darker shade on hover */
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777777;
        margin-top: 35px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
      }

      .footer p {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .accent-color {
        color: #007bff; /* A touch of blue for trust and stability */
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body
    style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 1rem; padding: 0; background-color: #f7f7f7; color: #495057; line-height: 1.6;"
  >
    <div
      class='container'
      style='width: 100%; max-width: 620px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;'
    >
      <div class='header' style='text-align: center; padding-bottom: 30px;'>
        <img
          src='cid:logo'
          alt='Sentria Logo'
          style='max-width: 160px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 25px;'
        />
        <h1
          style='margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 28px; color: #2c3e50; font-weight: 500;'
        >Welcome to Sentria!</h1>
      </div>
      <div
        class='content'
        style='padding: 25px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 17px; color: #555555;'
      >
        <p style='margin: 20px 0;'>We're so glad you've joined our community, a
          place where we come together to share vital information and support
          each other during challenging times.</p>
        <p style='margin: 20px 0;'>Your voice matters. By verifying your email,
          you'll be able to connect with others, share updates, and contribute
          to a network built on
          <span
            class='accent-color'
            style='color: #007bff; font-weight: bold;'
          >hope</span>
          and resilience.</p>
        <p style='margin: 20px 0;'>Please click the button below to activate
          your account and become a part of Sentria.</p>
        <div
          class='button-container'
          style='text-align: center; margin: 35px 0;'
        >
          <a
            href='{{verificationLink}}'
            class='button'
            style='display: inline-block; padding: 15px 35px; font-size: 18px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #28a745; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; transition: background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;'
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#1e7e34'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#28a745'"
          >Verify My Email & Join Sentria</a>
        </div>
        <p style='margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #777777;'>If you
          didn't sign up for Sentria, please disregard this email. No further
          action is needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div
        class='footer'
        style='text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #777777; margin-top: 35px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;'
      >
        <p style='margin: 8px 0;'>&copy;
          {{currentYear}}
          Sentria. Together, we are stronger.</p>
        <p style='margin: 8px 0;'>For support or inquiries, please visit our
          help center.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>